# Lovable Export Workflow

- Treat all Lovable dumps as raw reference code, not production app code.
- Keep raw exports under `frontend/lovable-dump/<date>-<feature>/`.
- Never wire Vite files directly into Next.js (`main.tsx`, `App.tsx`, `vite.config.ts`).
- Integrate by porting:
  - UI components -> `src/components/`
  - Utilities -> `src/lib/`
  - Page markup -> `src/app/...`
  - Static assets -> `public/...`
- Ensure all navigation buttons are connected to existing app routes (`/login`, `/signup`, etc.).
- After each integration, run lint/build checks and fix issues before finalizing.
